go_data.justification: DDX3 is described as a helicase, indicating it has RNA helicase activity.

go_data.term: negative regulation of NF-kappaB transcription factor activity
go_data.justification: DDX3 is part of the complexes containing TBK1 and IKKepsilon, which are involved in NF-kappaB signaling.
K7 inhibits IRF3 phosphorylation by binding to DDX3.
